text: San Jose is one of the 12 barangays of the municipality of San Jose, Dinagat Islands, Philippines. The barangay is south of the town proper of San Jose, in the Southern portion of the province.San Jose, Dinagat Islands - Google Maps It is also the location of the iconic Islander's Castle. ==See also== * Municipality of San Jose, Dinagat Islands * Islander's Castle == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage Category:Philippines geography stubs Category:Barangays of Dinagat Islands
